      </p>

      <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Execution Focused</h3>
          <p>Not just ideas—real workflows and outputs.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>Step-by-Step Guidance</h3>
          <p>Structured plans that are easy to follow.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3>AI-Powered Tools</h3>
          <p>Integrated tools for building faster.</p>
        </div>
